high_descs: Walk to the coffee table on the statue's side.
Grab the statue off the table.
Walk to the tall lamp to the left of the black sofa.
anns.task_desc: Examine a statue under a lamp's light.

high_descs: turn left to head across the room, at the end of the couch on your right take a left then another quick left to face the white slotted table
Pick up the golden man statue that is sitting on the slotted table
Turn left and go to the fireplace, at the fireplace take a right and walk to the tall floor lamp
anns.task_desc: Look at a statue under a lamp

high_descs: Turn left and walk toward the empty box on the sofa, then turn left again and walk to the statue on the coffee table.
Pick up the statue from the coffee table.
Turn right, walk to the fireplace, then turn right and walk to the floor lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a statue by the light of a floor lamp.
